=Beijing 北京 (Peking)=
==Literature==
===Monographs===
* [[Lin Yutang]]: Imperial Peking: Seven Centuries of China. London: Elek Books, 1961
* Martin Hürlimann: Peking und seine Geschichte. Zürich: Atlantis, 1976
* Chris Elder: Old Peking: City of the Ruler of the World. Hong Kong: Oxford University Press, 1997
* [[Susan Naquin]]: Peking: Temples and City Life, 1400-1900. London: University of California Press, 2000
* M.A. Aldrich: The Search for a Vanishing Beijing: A Guide to China's Capital Through the Ages. Hong Kong: Hong Kong University Press, 2006
* Stephen G. Haw: Bijing: A Concise History. London: Routledge, 2007
* Jasper Becker: City of Heavenly Tranquillity: Beijing in the History of China. London: Allen Lane, 2008
* [[Hok-lam Chan]]: Legends of the Building of Old Peking. Hong Kong: The Chinese University Press, 2008
===Traveloges===
* R.W. Swallow: Sidelights on Peking Life. Peking: The French Bookstore, 1927
* [[L. C. Arlington]] and [[William Lewisohn]]: In Search of Old Peking. New York: Paragon Book Reprint, 1967

